Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.70,0:00:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that easy to adjust the Uka-no-Mitama virus?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.07,0:00:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The process itself should be pretty much automated,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,so as long as the equipment still works, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.22,0:00:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They chose Uka-no-Mitama precisely because of how easy it is to update.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.94,0:00:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that a benign virus would end up becoming an actual disease...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought of it as an iron shield defending our food autonomy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but it ended up being a double-edged sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.83,0:00:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
