Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The security is still active...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.54,0:03:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Where can I find another way in...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! What a huge place...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this factory centrally manages the defense virus in order to distribute it to the entire Hokuriku area.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing that such a large-scale facility can continue to operate in a fully automated manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The bigger the prey, the easier it is to target.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially when you're wielding a poisoned needle strong enough to kill a whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This sort of tactic is just like Makishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably from Kougami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have seen us land.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In which case, he's nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsunemori speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect you to get here so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate the Bureau's resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the only one here capable of driving Makishima into a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already inside the facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, he's probably adjusting the Uka-no-Mitama virus right now using the equipment Kudama left in the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Or he might even have finished already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not going to let him have his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we don't have a moment to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to shut down the entire facility before he's able to distribute the Uka-no-Mitama that he tampered with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The Bureau has the authority to cut off the power to this facility, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That would halt not only its operation but its security system as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you want, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.38,0:05:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to use us to lift the security so that you can beat us to Makishima and kill him, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.86,0:05:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Makishima is trying to destroy this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:06:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The Bureau has only one choice right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.91,0:06:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then this country will be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.25,0:06:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I will save you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not let Kougami Shinya become a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let the fastest one win.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we have control of the security system transferred to us from the Ministry of Agriculture and Forestry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The process will take time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If Makishima finishes before us, it's checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice but to stop the facility itself, like Kougami said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunizuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already disabled the secondary power supply.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All we have to do now is cut off the primary power source.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I'd like to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.47,0:06:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When you encounter Kougami, if the Eliminator ends up activating because his Crime Coefficient is over 300,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,please don't shoot him. Call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:06:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a trump card up my sleeve for Kougami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we'll go after Makishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll help us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I need you to lock this gun in Paralyzer mode with the safety off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Dominator decides its enforcement mode based on the measured Crime Coefficients.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the foundation of the system that \Nmaintains public safety. It cannot be changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.42,0:07:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If we are to fight Makishima, we need weapons that can do the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to protect ourselves too, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can't use the Dominators, we'll have no choice but to depend on more primitive weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If worst comes to worst, we may end up killing Makishima with those weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your lack of resourcefulness would be at fault in that scenario, not us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.35,0:08:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Our abilities are limited and the probability that we will capture Makishima alive without problems is hardly 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're able to grant an exception here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,we may be able to improve that chance a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about which course of action offers the most benefit.{delays here courtesy of minami}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're good at calculating risk and reward, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From now until Makishima Shougo is captured,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}we will grant an exception on the applicable terminal device.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The safety will remain off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mode is Non-Lethal Paralyzer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.37,0:08:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, please pay close attention to how you use it to ensure the other detectives do not find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been acting strange ever since the Chief called you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened, but are you sure you can shoulder that burden alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're acting the same as Kougami did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:09:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna see you push yourself\N too hard as an Inspector and burn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then would you like to check my Crime Coefficient?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Please point the Dominator at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll delete the record using my authority as an Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crime Coefficient is 24.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An Inspector registered at the Criminal Investigation Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm someone the System wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunizuka, please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll cut off the power to the entire facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad, Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, Makishima's attempt at bio-terrorism ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.39,0:10:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't the rational thing be to escape immediately?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not so sure about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,True, Makishima has carefully considered his actions up to this point,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but that doesn't necessarily mean he acts purely on logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that he'll stick to his plan even now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's any way he can succeed, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:10:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the emergency power supply?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, we're just blocking his use of it from outside, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That means it can still be manually rebooted via the control board inside the facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's his only chance for getting the power back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we wait for him at the central control room, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.83,0:11:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't rule out the possibility that he'll simply try to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.91,0:11:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time for us to make a detour.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's split in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the control room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Ginoza, please check the university's lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.59,0:11:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with Inspector Tsunemori.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If we work with Shion at Headquarters via the main security console,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.64,0:11:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,we might be able to get access to the security cameras here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll be in charge of chasing him down, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.09,0:11:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't make that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our job as men to take on the dirty work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:11:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen at the Ministry of Welfare?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it seem that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like you could take on the world right now, but at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you look like that whole world's\N weighing on your shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving up here wouldn't resolve anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have to press forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how small it may be, there's still hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I don't give up on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.53,0:12:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can continue to be a detective until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When you joined us as a new Inspector,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,my first impression was that you were a naïve little girl who couldn't possibly be fit for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But in fact, I've never been further from the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:12:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd trust you with my life, Inspector Tsunemori.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You think too highly of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.97,0:13:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we made it in time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But do you think Makishima will really come this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right... Why isn't there anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.07,0:13:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\move(640,604,640,634,2575,2700)}There's someone who can foresee Makishima's
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.07,0:13:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,actions more accurately than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If we were right, I'd expect to see Kougami here already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.99,0:13:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be something we're overlooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I need to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here and now? What's on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.91,0:14:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You helped Kougami escape, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an old man, you know? Cut me some slack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that it's okay for Kougami to take the law into his own hands, as long as evil is defeated as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the savage, selfish idea of "justice" shared by old-fashioned hunting dogs like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kougami is the one you're relying on to get the job done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't expect anything from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You think there's no chance in hell I can capture Makishima, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.54,0:14:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kogami is a latent criminal as well as an Enforcer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He and I are cut from the same cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're still on a different path than we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly do think that's for the best. From the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of justification is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A culprit runs, and detectives go after him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we assumed would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:14:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:15:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But Makishima looks at things differently than we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He understands just how much of a bind we're in,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.85,0:15:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,better than we do ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.13,0:15:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginoza and Masaoka are in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.89,0:15:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait! It's dangerous to go by yourself!{Take this.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If Makishima comes, whatever you do, don't let him touch the emergency power supply!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy the whole console if you need to!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginoza! Inspector Ginoza?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobuchika!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Are you trying to blow us both up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I'd do something stupid like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let that man go! You must stop him at any cost, Enforcer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a detective! Fulfill your duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you let the culprit get away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a detective, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not fit to be called a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my son, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes... look just the same as mine did...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,when I was your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.31,0:19:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So you finally ditched that fake justice \Nand developed some real bloodlust, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're everything I hoped you'd be after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.26,0:19:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I never had any hopes for you to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:19:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act so indifferent after coming this far for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the arrogance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing exceptional about you.{b-baka}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a piece of garbage, forsaken by society.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you feel bitter after being rejected by your peers and excluded from the community, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.07,0:20:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You just can't stand to be on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.97,0:20:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no different from a kid whining about not wanting to be left out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.20,0:20:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure do say some funny things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm the only one who's left out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Who {\i1}isn't{\i0} alone in this society?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The time when our connection to others was the basis of our selves is long gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no place for communities in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,where everyone is watched over by the system and lives within the system's standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone stays in their own little cell,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and the system tames them by giving them each their own personal serenity.
